Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*最棒的圣诞 终于来到*\N{\fs38}*Last king christmas last arrived*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*在圣诞这一天到来*\N{\fs38}*On the christmas christmas*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这火腿简直人间美味\N{\fs38}Mmm. Jerry, you are really giving it to this ham.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐 嘿\N{\fs38}Um, merry christmas. Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸妈这么多年才来一次\N{\fs38}My parents are coming over for the first time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱能把手里的玩意儿都收了 有点生气吗\N{\fs38}Can we stow the gadgets and look alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你爸妈面前表现的有点生气\N{\fs38}Alive? For your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 真好笑\N{\fs38}Mm, good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛\N{\fs38}Hey, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.88,0:00:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛\N{\fs38}You"Hey, man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个节日就是要有人情味儿\N{\fs38}This holiday is about humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我还以为是什么半神的生日之类的\N{\fs38}You know, I thought it was about being born half-god or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 所有电子设备都给我放进这个袜子里\N{\fs38}Whatever. All electronic items are going in the stocking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 我才不会把手机给你\N{\fs38}Dad, I'm not giving you my phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖放进来 不然我就去注册Facebook\N{\fs38}Put it in the stocking, summer, or I'm joining facebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚯嚯嚯 大家好\N{\fs38}A-ho, ho, ho, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看是"啧啧啧"吧\N{\fs38}More like "Whoa, whoa, whoa."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.25,0:01:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是搞啥 我爸妈马上要来了\N{\fs38}What is this? My parents are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淡定 Jerry\N{\fs38}Calm down, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Reuben 我一老朋友\N{\fs38}This is Reuben, an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍珠港\N{\fs38}Pearl harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我每年给他做一次医学诊断\N{\fs38}I check in on him once a year and give him a little medical evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 真感人\N{\fs38}Aww! Dad, that is so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.09,0:01:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 真感人 我不懂了\N{\fs38}Yeah, it is. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韩国\N{\fs38}Korea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心你的圣诞聚会 Jerry\N{\fs38}Don't worry about your C-christmas, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟Reuben去我的工作间\N{\fs38}I'll be with Reuben in my workshop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就好好在著名的Phil Collins所谓"天堂"里过着吧\N{\fs38}while you guys are having another day in Phil Collins' proverbial paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}Phil Collins 《Another Day in Paradise》 讲述跟穷困的人们比起来我们过得就像天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不识庐山真面目\N{\fs38}Huh. You think you know a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸妈来啦\N{\fs38}Okay, there's my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.15,0:01:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看电视 别玩手机 别碰电脑\N{\fs38}Now, remember no tv, no phones, no laptops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好增进一下感情 就和传统的犹太人过周六一样\N{\fs38}We are connecting this Christmas, like old-school Jews on a saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}犹太教的安息日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fs38}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐 儿子\N{\fs38}Merry christmas, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs38}Uh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有事吗\N{\fs38}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 这是Jacob\N{\fs38}Jerry, this is Jacob.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没收到我们的短信吗\N{\fs38}Didn't you get our text message?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是Jerry吧\N{\fs38}You must be Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这围裙很好看啊\N{\fs38}That's a fine-looking apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威廉姆斯索诺玛的吗\N{\fs38}Williams-sonoma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}美国高端家居用品零售商
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:01:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒想呢\N{\fs38}I wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过谢谢\N{\fs38}But thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.62,0:02:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我父母的朋友吗\N{\fs38}So, you're a... friend of the family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们眼中 他是家人\N{\fs38}Uh, the way we see it, he's a part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fs38}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸和癌症擦肩而过\N{\fs38}After your father's brush with cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叔叔也走了 所以我们决定重新审视我们过去的人生\N{\fs38}and losing your uncle, we looked at life and wondered, how have we spent it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和剩下的时光\N{\fs38}And how do we spend the rest of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们死的时候会是什么样的\N{\fs38}What are we going to be when we die
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是充满了恐惧和怀疑\N{\fs38}a list of fears and questions
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是过了充实的一生\N{\fs38}or a collection of real experiences?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Joyce 真了不起\N{\fs38}Holy crap. Joyce, that's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后Jacob出现了 我们开始重新享受生活\N{\fs38}Then Jacob came into our lives, and... we're learning to live again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.76,0:02:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们三个一起\N{\fs38}All three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fs38}Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来点蛋奶酒吗\N{\fs38}Eggnog?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.79,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才像话嘛 这爷们有围裙还有蛋奶酒\N{\fs38}Now we are talking! This man's got the apron and the eggnog, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Joyce Leonard\N{\fs38}Hi, Joyce. Leonard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\fs38}Merry christmas, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 能过来一下吗\N{\fs38}Morty, a moment of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他快不行了 Morty\N{\fs38}He's in bad shape, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 Rick 你干了啥\N{\fs38}Aw, geez, Rick. What'd you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 Morty 你把我当成什么了\N{\fs38}Gee, thanks, Morty. W-w-what kind of monster do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.97,0:02:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在救他的命\N{\fs38}I-I-I'm sitting here trying to save the guy's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你帮忙\N{\fs38}I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找Xenon Bloom博士\N{\fs38}I want you to find Dr. Xenon Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道是怎么回事\N{\fs38}He'll know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.10,0:02:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去哪哪哪哪儿找Bloom博士啊\N{\fs38}Uh, w-w-w-where where do I find dr. Bloom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reuben\N{\fs38}In Reuben.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明尼苏达的Reuben吗\N{\fs38}Reuben, Minne-minnesota?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桌子上的Reuben\N{\fs38}Reuben on the table, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没时间让你刨根问底了\N{\fs38}Look, I-I-I I don't have time for you to wrap your little walnut around everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束之前屏住呼吸 不然你的肺就完了\N{\fs38}Just hold your breath until the process is over or your lungs will collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么结\N{\fs38}What proc...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 Morty呢\N{\fs38}Hey, dad, where's Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.04,0:03:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在忙\N{\fs38}He's busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 能听见吗\N{\fs38}Morty, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往北走\N{\fs38}Head north.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick我这是在哪儿\N{\fs38}Rick, where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按我注射的位置 你应该在入口的南边\N{\fs38}Depending on my aim, you should be just south of the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥入口\N{\fs38}Entrance to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎 Morty\N{\fs38}Welcome, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到人体公园\N{\fs38}Welcome... ... to Anatomy park!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.86,1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz2.232\fs48\3c&H181B6D&\pos(648,254)}人体公园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(642,716)}这是我和Bloom博士一起搞的一个小副业\N{\fs38}It's a little business venture I've been cooking up on the side with Dr. Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体内的主题公园\N{\fs38}An amusement park inside a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞科学很费钱的 这玩意多多少少能补贴一点\N{\fs38}Science isn't ch-cheap, morty. This should really help put a dent in the overhead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 太不可思议了\N{\fs38}Oh, my god! This is insane!
