Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胰之海盗\N{\fs38}Pirates of the pancreas?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.08,5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz6.969\fs36\pos(960,384)}胰之海盗→\N就在腹腔乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.02,0:03:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对最后一个有什么意见吗\N{\fs38}You got a problem with that last one, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(672,718)}没有\N{\fs38}Huh? No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是看到什么就念出来而已\N{\fs38}I'm just reading'em out loud in the order that I'm seeing'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我有点敏感\N{\fs38}Okay. All right. If I sounded a little defensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为胰之海盗是我的宝贝\N{\fs38}It's because pirates of the pancreas was my baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想建这个的时候遇到了不少阻力 Morty\N{\fs38}You know, I got I got a lot of pushback when I pitched it, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还是有点护短\N{\fs38}I guess I'm still a little defensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.44,0:04:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之快去找Bloom博士\N{\fs38}Let's just find dr. Bloom, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在肝脏发现了求救信号\N{\fs38}I-I'm picking up a distress signal in the liver, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去肝那儿\N{\fs38}Proceed to the liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.81,6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(576,556)}肺叶弹射
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.81,9,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1102,536)}结肠漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.81,6,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(834,526)}{\c&HB5FFE5&}鬼肝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:08.81,7,,0,0,0,,{\frz22.52\pos(774,242)}脑皮层木马
