Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.14,4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz8.326\pos(664,280)}前往 下腹乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前方到站 肝脏\N{\fs38}Arriving at... ... liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心站台间隙\N{\fs38}Mind the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:24.18,10,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz6.8\fs36\move(142,554,1086,484,100,3200)\fad(100,500)}灰尘见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿好恐怖啊 Rick\N{\fs38}It's really scary in here, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝的情况不太好\N{\fs38}The liver's under maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reuben这几年过得很苦\N{\fs38}Reuben's seen some rough years, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说三道四\N{\fs38}Don't judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子过得好的人是不会同意在自己体内修一座主题公园的\N{\fs38}You don't agree to have a theme park built inside you if your life's going great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:29.20,11,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs62\pos(628,378)}鬼肝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 有妖怪啊\N{\fs38}Rick! It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 Morty\N{\fs38}No, no, no. Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿唯一的妖怪只有酗酗酗酒\N{\fs38}The only monster here is alco...... holism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是个机械狼人\N{\fs38}That is an animatronic werewolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs38}Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说\N{\fs38}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪儿来的\N{\fs38}Where'd you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我我外公Rick让我来的\N{\fs38}My my my grandpa Rick sent me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poncho 够了\N{\fs38}Poncho! That's quite enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 这是Poncho\N{\fs38}Morty, that's Poncho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Roger和Annie\N{\fs38}This is Roger and Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Xenon Bloom博士\N{\fs38}And I am Dr. Xenon Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Bloom 我是Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, Bloom, it's Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底出什么事儿了\N{\fs38}What the hell's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道 整个安全系统都停止运作了\N{\fs38}I don't know why, but the entire security system has shut down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎展品也逃出来了\N{\fs38}and I'm afraid... the exhibits are unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展品\N{\fs38}Exhibits?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人 人体公园最吸引人的部分\N{\fs38}Anatomy park's greatest attraction, young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是音乐 食物 或者\N{\fs38}isn't the music or the food or the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胰之海盗\N{\fs38}Pirates of the pancreas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话注意点\N{\fs38}Watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是人体内最凶恶宏伟的病原体活体博物馆\N{\fs38}It is, first and foremost, a living museum of humanity's most noble and ferocious diseases.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病原体\N{\fs38}Diseases?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 博士 最新消息\N{\fs38}Hey, doc. I got news for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的活体博物馆现在正式成为野生动物园了\N{\fs38}Your living museum is officially a wild safari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是甲肝病毒 快跑\N{\fs38}Hepatitis A! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西要吃进嘴里去啊\N{\fs38}Oh, the food goes in your mouth, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 Jacob\N{\fs38}Oh, Jacob.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 Jacob\N{\fs38}I-I'm sorry, Jacob.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不太明白 你和我父母\N{\fs38}I-I guess I'm still confused about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底具体是啥关系 怎么开始的\N{\fs38}the precise nature and origin of your relationship with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照顾他们的生活起居吗\N{\fs38}Are you, like, uh are you, like, their caretaker? Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,细节我们待会儿再说\N{\fs38}We can go into detail later, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么可隐瞒的\N{\fs38}Now, wait. Th-there's no point to secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论生死都要坦诚\N{\fs38}Let's all live and die honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈妈和我共度了四十年人生 从身心到灵魂\N{\fs38}Your mother and I have shared 40 years of each other, mind, body, and soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当心和灵魂永远相依\N{\fs38}and when minds and souls are joined for eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而永恒的死亡在招手\N{\fs38}and when eternity is At the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就该放身体自由\N{\fs38}it's an invitation to let go of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去分享和尝试\N{\fs38}and an opportunity to share and experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 你到底在说什么\N{\fs38}Dad, please. What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管说的是什么 听上去都很美好 Leonard 我们支持你\N{\fs38}Whatever it is, it's beautiful, Leonard, and we support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己支持去吧\N{\fs38}Hey, speak for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 你这好像马上要说Jacob是你的情人一样\N{\fs38}because it sounds like you're about to say jacob is your lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不\N{\fs38}No, no, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jacob是你妈妈的情人\N{\fs38}Jacob is your mother's lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候我坐在椅子上看他们\N{\fs38}I watch them sometimes from a chair
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候在衣柜里 基本上都穿着超人服\N{\fs38}and sometimes from a closet, almost always dressed as superman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 这火腿是你的杰作吧\N{\fs38}Jerry, this ham has got to be all you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是美味至极\N{\fs38}It's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.74,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有人情味儿啊 节日快乐 爸\N{\fs38}Happy human holiday, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝炎病毒不会跟进呼吸系统里来的\N{\fs38}Hepatitis won't follow us into the respiratory system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:54.68,12,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(882,138)}肺泡林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪\N{\fs38}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,含气量下降了百分之二十\N{\fs38}Airflow is down 20%.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大脑肯定供氧不足\N{\fs38}So, the brain isn't getting enough oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪安全系统停掉了\N{\fs38}That's why security's offline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们最好去看看\N{\fs38}Well, I guess we better check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 等等我\N{\fs38}Hey! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.01,0:07:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上\N{\fs38}Put that back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果上到支气管那的过道去 就能找找是哪儿堵住了\N{\fs38}If we got up to the bronchial catwalk, we could look for a blockage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去\N{\fs38}I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逞英雄 孩子\N{\fs38}Don't be a hero, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\fs38}I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯属找乐子\N{\fs38}I'm doing it because it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不该在这儿\N{\fs38}We shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何情况下都不要开枪\N{\fs38}Whatever you do, do not fire that thing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须救下Reuben\N{\fs38}We must save Reuben.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我毕生的心血\N{\fs38}This is my life's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs38}It's all right, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎所有人的肺里都会有这种细菌\N{\fs38}Nearly all human lungs contain a strain of these bacteria, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘢痕组织能抑制它们的活动\N{\fs38}The scar tissue keeps them... Dormant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 快下来\N{\fs38}Morty, get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是什么\N{\fs38}Oh, what are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肺结核杆菌冲过来了\N{\fs38}Tuberculosis coming in fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的子弹\N{\fs38}Not faster than a bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你知道你干了什么吗\N{\fs38}No! Do you know what you've done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.24,0:08:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去消化道\N{\fs38}Get to the digestive tract!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开始咳嗽了\N{\fs38}He's coughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死\N{\fs38}Don't let me die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深呼吸 Reuben\N{\fs38}Just take a deep breath, Reuben.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会死的\N{\fs38}You're not gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\fs38}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫 Alexand\N{\fs38}My name is... Alexand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick Reunben得了肺结核\N{\fs38}Rick R-r-reuben's got tuberculosis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, great work, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就治好他\N{\fs38}Okay, I'll just cure it and then
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我治不好死人\N{\fs38}Well, I can't cure death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不妙 Morty\N{\fs38}This is bad, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们被困在一死人的身体里了\N{\fs38}You're trapped in a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果情况继续恶化 对自己好点\N{\fs38}Listen, if the situation keeps darkening, do yourself a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去胰之海盗玩玩\N{\fs38}And pop by pirates of the pancreas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显我不太客观 但我觉得真的超级棒\N{\fs38}Obviously I'm biased, but I think it's great, morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.02,0:08:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一堆海盗围着胰腺跑啊跑\N{\fs38}It's a bunch of pirates running around a pancreas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也没刻意美化 Morty\N{\fs38}We don't whitewash it, either, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些海盗都特吓人\N{\fs38}I mean, the pirates are really rapey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一要务当然是把你们救出来\N{\fs38}The top priority is to get, you know, you guys out of there, but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果实在是出不来了 一定要去玩玩啊\N{\fs38}I'm just saying, if that becomes impossible, please, you gotta treat yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.07,0:08:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 什么东西这么难闻\N{\fs38}Oh, man. W-w-w-what is that horrible smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熊猫快餐吗\N{\fs38}You mean the panda express?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs38}美国中式快餐连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑 我开玩笑的\N{\fs38}Kidding. I-I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体开始收缩并且产生气体了\N{\fs38}The body is beginning to constrict and fill with gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一具死尸里面啊\N{\fs38}We're inside a corpse, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体公园完蛋了\N{\fs38}Anatomy park is doomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管公园了 博士\N{\fs38}Forget about the park, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么出去\N{\fs38}How do we get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消化道就是疏散(排泄)通道\N{\fs38}The digestive tract is the evacuation route.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笑点有懂吗\N{\fs38}Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结肠有一个应急站点 能把我们变回原来的大小\N{\fs38}There's an emergency station in the colon with a ray that can enlarge us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去结肠\N{\fs38}Everybody, head for the colon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.65,0:09:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还得听一个十二岁小孩儿的\N{\fs38}Now I'm taking orders from a 12-year-old boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 那些有结核杆菌的液泡是被人故意弄破的\N{\fs38}Morty, the scar sacs containing the tuberculosis were sabotaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事绝对是内鬼干的\N{\fs38}This disaster was an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盯着点Annie\N{\fs38}Keep your eye on Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在西班牙油条摊的时候被经理记了几次过\N{\fs38}She was written up several times by her manager at the churro stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.10,0:09:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进了肠道先往左 然后往右 再往左 以此类推\N{\fs38}Intestines are ahead to the left, then to the right, then left, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥 我其实十四了 所以 你懂的...\N{\fs38}Hey, just so you know, i-I-I'm actually 14. So, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是十二\N{\fs38}Not 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他刚才说我十二\N{\fs38}You know, because he just said I was 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 挺好的\N{\fs38}Oh. Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哦 出师不利啊 Morty\N{\fs38}Oof. Ugh. Morty. Strike one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*奇妙之路呀食物之旅*\N{\fs38}*It's a road of wonder, a trail of food*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*是好是坏都消化干净*\N{\fs38}*It's a pathway to break up the bad and good*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*吸收剩下的全排出去*\N{\fs38}*It's a tube that digests and then sends out the rest*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*小小的小肠呀*\N{\fs38}*It's a small, small intestine*
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还得走好一阵呢\N{\fs38}It goes on like this for miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就到大肠啦\N{\fs38}Then we get to the large intestine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 有动静\N{\fs38}Shh! I hear something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动\N{\fs38}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们不动 淋球菌是看不见我们的\N{\fs38}Gonorrhea can't see us if we don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦不对 记成霸王龙了\N{\fs38}Wait, I was wrong. I was thinking of a T. Rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fs38}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.72,0:10:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就是活靶子啊\N{\fs38}We're sitting ducks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,博士 现在尸体里开始产生气体了是吗\N{\fs38}Doc, didn't you say that the body was filling with gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 怎么了\N{\fs38}Yes. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 你真是个天才\N{\fs38}Kid, you're a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯啦\N{\fs38}Are you mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都躲到这儿来\N{\fs38}Everybody, in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 淋球菌 尝尝灼痛(淋病症状之一)的感觉吧\N{\fs38}Hey, gonorrhea! How's this for a burning sensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*鼓手敲啊敲*\N{\fs38}*Drummer drum drum*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*敲啊敲啊敲*\N{\fs38}*drum drum drum drum drum drum drum drum drum*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*圣诞小鼓*\N{\fs38}*Christmas drums*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱啊 Summer\N{\fs38}Oh, sing it, Summer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.25,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*圣诞小鼓*\N{\fs38}*Christmas drums*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- *小哥在敲*  - 我真喜欢听你唱歌\N{\fs38}- *Being played by a bo-o-o-y* - oh I love to hear you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 别这样 你不就想要这样吗\N{\fs38}Jerry, come on. This is what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的 Beth 愿不能乱许\N{\fs38}I get it, Beth. Be careful what you wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿了你的iPad我遭报应了\N{\fs38}I'm being punished for taking your iPad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 别多想了\N{\fs38}What? Jerry, let that stuff go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前是我不对\N{\fs38}I'm sorry I was a bitch earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受当下吧\N{\fs38}Let's just be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Summer  - Ethan\N{\fs38}- Summer! - Ethan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来干嘛\N{\fs38}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几个小时我一直在给你发短信\N{\fs38}I've been texting you for hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么鬼\N{\fs38}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机不在我身上 我在过有人情味儿的节日呢\N{\fs38}I don't have my phone! I'm doing a human holiday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有考虑过我的感受吗\N{\fs38}Well, did you even consider how that might make me feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的感受\N{\fs38}How you feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事儿都非得和你扯上关系吗\N{\fs38}Why is everything always happening to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer 你有男朋友\N{\fs38}Summer, do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 Summer 你有吗\N{\fs38}Yeah, do you, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊 Ethan 我有吗\N{\fs38}I don't know, Ethan. Do I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 无意冒犯 但是你真得和家人好好增进下感情啊\N{\fs38}Jerry, no disrespect, but you really need to connect more with your family, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该能用备用电源启动放大射线\N{\fs38}I should be able to access the backup generator to get the growth ray online.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.53,0:12:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果行得通 几分钟内我们就能回到正常大小了\N{\fs38}If it works, we'll be regular-sized in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但愿Reuben现在不是躺在白地毯或者垫子上啥的\N{\fs38}I just hope Reuben's not in a room with white carpets or upholstery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西\N{\fs38}What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,括约肌大坝\N{\fs38}The sphincter dam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Reuben开始大小便失禁以后我们修的\N{\fs38}We built it when Reuben became incontinent,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.49,0:12:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他死了以后就承受不住了\N{\fs38}but it was not designed to hold a corpse load.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就好了\N{\fs38}I've almost got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都站到圈里去\N{\fs38}Everybody, move inside the circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poncho 你包里这是什么\N{\fs38}Poncho? What is this in your backpack?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是黑死病病毒\N{\fs38}That's bubonic plague!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你带着这个做什么 Poncho\N{\fs38}What are you doing with that, Poncho?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我退后\N{\fs38}Everybody, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Poncho 你这个混蛋\N{\fs38}Poncho, you son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把结核菌放了出来 好从我这儿偷东西\N{\fs38}You released the tuberculosis so you could steal from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错\N{\fs38}That's right, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一大票人愿意为了削减人口出大价钱\N{\fs38}A lot of people would pay top dollar to decimate the population.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我直接卖给出价最高的人\N{\fs38}I'll take the highest bidder
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地组织 朝鲜 共和党人 圣地兄弟会\N{\fs38}Al-qaeda, north korea, republicans, shriners,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健身的秃子\N{\fs38}balding men that work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看日本少年动画才能性奋的死宅\N{\fs38}people on the internet that are only turned on by cartoons of japanese teenagers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都比给你干活强\N{\fs38}anything is better than working for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个自命不凡 疏忽大意\N{\fs38}you pompous, negligent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,节日津贴就给发iTunes礼品卡的傻...\N{\fs38}iTunes-gift-card-as-a-holiday-bonus-giving mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了吧\N{\fs38}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开\N{\fs38}Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊\N{\fs38}You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要炸了 快跑\N{\fs38}It's gonna burst! Go! Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脚卡住了\N{\fs38}My foot is stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 你们走\N{\fs38}It's okay! It's okay. Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.72,0:13:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我的家人我爱他们\N{\fs38}Tell my family I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.69,0:13:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不太好找 因为我老婆留着娘家姓\N{\fs38}They may be hard to find'cause my wife kept her last name
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.87,0:13:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子也随她姓\N{\fs38}and she made the kids take it, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没啥法子 不然你们...\N{\fs38}So, I-I don't know, you can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.93,0:13:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你一个问题 Ethan\N{\fs38}Let me ask you a question, Ethan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.86,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的愤怒从何而来\N{\fs38}Where's the anger coming from, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Summer是个贱人\N{\fs38}From Summer being a total bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在气什么\N{\fs38}Where's the anger coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥 有一次带我去钓鱼 然后在树丛里\N{\fs38}My brother... took me fishing once... in the bushes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不行\N{\fs38}I can't... I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.33,0:13:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他像对女孩子那样\N{\fs38}He made me feel like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他让我成了一个女孩\N{\fs38}I...he made me a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.83,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有改变你\N{\fs38}He didn't make you anything, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是你\N{\fs38}You are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是她\N{\fs38}She is who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去她那里吧 带着崭新的自己\N{\fs38}Now, you go to her... brand-new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs38}Come here, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我很抱歉 Ethan\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. I'm so sorry, Ethan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs38}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很爱你\N{\fs38}I love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又做到了 亲爱的\N{\fs38}You did it again, cubbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来\N{\fs38}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下 我讨厌这样\N{\fs38}No! Stop! I hate this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞节可不在乎你讨厌什么 儿子\N{\fs38}Well, Christmas doesn't revolve around what you hate, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我讨厌圣诞节\N{\fs38}Well, then I hate Christmas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的人情味儿 你们真是又逊又恶心\N{\fs38}Enjoy being human! You guys are gross and lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫Reuben Ridley\N{\fs38}My name's Reuben Ridley.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们现在在我的身体里\N{\fs38}You're inside me right now, but
